@startuml dao_pattern

title 数据访问对象(DAO)模式类图 - 飞机大战分数记录持久化

class ScoreRecord {
    -String playerName
    -int score
    -String time
    +ScoreRecord()
    +ScoreRecord(playerName, score, time)
    +getPlayerName() : String
    +setPlayerName(playerName) : void
    +getScore() : int
    +setScore(score) : void
    +getTime() : String
    +setTime(time) : void
}

interface ScoreDao {
    +getAllScoreRecords() : ArrayList<ScoreRecord>
    +doAdd(ScoreRecord scoreRecord) : void
    +doDelete(index) : void
}

class ScoreDaoByFile {
    -String filePath
    +setFilePath(filePath) : void
    +getAllScoreRecords() : ArrayList<ScoreRecord>
    +doAdd(ScoreRecord scoreRecord) : void
    +doDelete(index) : void
    -readFile(filePath) : ArrayList<ScoreRecord>
    -writeFile(filePath, scoreRecords) : void
}

class Game {
    -int score
    #String daoFilePath
    #String difficultyName
    -MusicController musicController
    --
    -gameOverAction() : void
}

ScoreDao <|.. ScoreDaoByFile : 实现
Game .right.> ScoreDao : 依赖
ScoreDaoByFile -left-> ScoreRecord : 使用

@enduml
